coming front slit number 1,

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:36.116
then this is the distribution
I get, which is I-1.

00:19:36.116 --> 00:19:41.030
If I close the upper one
and open only the lower one,

00:19:41.030 --> 00:19:45.410
I get a distribution
which is I-2.

00:19:45.410 --> 00:19:49.480
And this light
source, essentially

00:19:49.480 --> 00:19:53.780
