00:20:09.770 --> 00:20:13.370
And if I do this
experiment result--

00:20:13.370 --> 00:20:17.730
if I block one of the slits,
this is the distribution, I-1

00:20:17.730 --> 00:20:22.400
and I-2 and now I'm
