There's another way to do this.

00:24:51.430 --> 00:24:53.870
Experimental result
number four--

00:24:53.870 --> 00:24:57.980
so what will happen
if I use this formula

00:24:57.980 --> 00:25:04.100
E equal to h bar mu equal
