00:26:04.920 --> 00:26:07.620
Can anybody guess what
is going to happen?

00:26:10.940 --> 00:26:14.670
With a result like
experimental result number one,

00:26:14.670 --> 00:26:18.870
when I go to extremely
low intensity?

00:26:18.870 --> 00:26:24.330
Or my result will be like
experimental result number two?

00:26:24.330 --> 00:26:29.620
Because each electrons
are bothered,

00:26:29.620 --> 00:26:37.170
are heated, by the emission
