00:26:37.170 --> 00:26:40.330
Anybody want to try?

00:26:40.330 --> 00:26:42.180
Just guess, no?

00:26:42.180 --> 00:26:43.796
One or two?

00:26:43.796 --> 00:26:47.325
Or a mixture of them?

00:26:47.325 --> 00:26:49.200
AUDIENCE: Be like two.

00:26:49.200 --> 00:26:50.940
YEN-JIE LEE: The
